\C[2]The enemies in the vicinity became docile
after being able to control this Nest Stone with
magic\C[1]!

Do you want to release the control of the Nest
Stone? If you release it, nearby enemies will
attack.
Released the control of the Nest Stone!

\C[2]I controlled this Nest Stone with magic!
\C[1]The nearby enemies became docile!
Hmm... now, how should I be called, I wonder?

I heard there's a stupid demon here who's being
worshipped like a god and getting carried away. I
wonder if they really exist~?
Now... what should I be called...

I can hear you, so come out quickly, Baretta. Come
out quickly, Baretta.
Finally, we meet face to face.

A mysterious creature... that seems to see through
me...

What kind of being are you...? How did you manage
to see through everyone's magic...? This power...
it's both fascinating and dangerous.

Giiiyaaaaa!!! It's a lieeeee!!! Me... it's
meeeee!!!

Phew, I managed to defeat that huge monster that
was causing such a rampage.
